text: Benjamin van Niekerk (born 4 January 1996) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mpumalanga in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 14 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Mpumalanga cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
